This sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.

This foil sticker was autographed by professional player Vincent Cervoni playing for Team EnVyUs at MLG Columbus 2016.\n\n50% of the proceeds from the sale of this sticker support the included players and organizations.
